name: Origami Astar
description:
Astar (commonly spelt Aster) comes from the Greek for 'star' and perfectly describes this range of paper brooches, created using Chinese Paper Folding techniques. Each brooch is made up of 48 modular pieces, constructed together in a unique and striking design.

These paper pieces are made from recycled and reclaimed materials and each individual piece is unique and lovingly hand crafted, coated in a layer of matt varnish to create a durable piece of jewellery without losing the quality of the paper.

This stunning feature brooch is 7cm x 7cm x 1.5cm. The sunburst was created from folded paper from upcycled vintage books from Katie’s vast collection which she uses to invent beautiful, unusual jewellery.

name: Vintage Bronze Hairpins
description:
Handmade from vintage sheet music carefully encased in glass with a beautiful, decorative bronze surround. Accessorise you hair with vintage flair with these pretty vintage hairpins. 

One purchase contains two hairpins approximately 2.5cm long with a 1.5cm cabochon. The hairpins and setting are antique bronze plated (both lead and nickel free) with glass cabochon. 

The feature centre was created using vintage sheet music from Katie’s vast collection of antique books and vintage music score which she uses to invent beautiful, unusual jewellery.

name: Vintage Bronze Ring
description:
Using her own vocal sheet music and other rescued tomes, Katie captures the emotion of each musical piece and encases it within glass and antique bronze. Subtle blue/green hues are visible on the surface of the music, adding a distinctive aged look to the collection.

THIS SALE is for a Treble Clef OR Bass Clef Ring (adjustable size), approximately 2cm x 2cm with a 1.5cm face, with antique bronze plated setting (lead and nickel free) and glass cabochon. The ring was created using recycled vintage sheet music.

PLEASE NOTE: you will receive a custom made ring similar to the one pictured, however sheet music style and colouring may vary due to the handmade nature of this product.

name: Vintage Bronze Necklace
description:
Inspired by a love of music and aged jewellery, Katie's latest collection 'Vintage Bronze' was released Christmas 2011 and met with huge demand. 

Using her own vocal sheet music and other rescued tomes, Katie captures the emotion of each musical piece and encases it within glass and antique bronze. Subtle blue/green hues are visible on the surface of the music, adding a distinctive aged look to the collection.

THIS SALE is for the necklace '____', approximately 2.5cm x 3.5cm x 0.5cm, with antique bronze plated 18" chain and setting (both lead and nickel free) and glass cabochon. The pendant was created using vintage sheet music rescued from a house clearance.

name: Origami Sunburst Necklace
description:
Sunbursts are made using origami paper folding techniques to create beautiful, one of a kind pieces of jewellery. They consist of 48 individually folded modular pieces, lovingly crafted to create intricately detailed shapes.

Made from recycled and reclaimed materials each individual piece is unique and lovingly hand crafted, coated in a layer of matt varnish to create a durable piece of jewellery without losing the quality of the paper.

THIS SALE is for a single-coloured, approximately 7cm x 7cm x 1.5cm CUSTOM Sunburst necklace.

Choose from either an antique bronze or silver plated 18" chain.
